file.name: http_api_description.yaml
file.content:
Resources:
  HttpApi:
    Type: AWS::Serverless::HttpApi
    Properties:
      DefinitionBody:
        openapi: "3.0.1"
        paths:
          "/foo": {}
      Description: my description

  Function:
    Type: AWS::Serverless::Function
    Properties:
      Runtime: python3.7
      Handler: index.handler
      CodeUri: s3://bucket/key
      Events:
        Api:
          Type: HttpApi
          Properties:
            ApiId: HttpApi
